---

<Layout title="Brand Design + Strategy">



  <ContainerFW>
    <SectionEmail>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Brand design + strategies for local business.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Effective marketing is simply no accident, not even close. We design brands that seemlessly 
        convert their target audience. Validated brand strategy, direction and design. Ready for global scale.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={PagecoverHero}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SectionEmail>
  </ContainerFW>

  <ContainerFW>
    <GallerySlider />
  </ContainerFW>

  <ContainerXL>
    <SectionHeadImg>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Brand direction + strategy.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Based on the Gold Coast and redefining the way businesses can manage their brand. Come back to Earth for 
        air and remember the good old days of freelancers you can rely on. If your office is located on the Gold Coast 
        we come directly to you, once a month to improve the speed of development. While also always being only a click away 
        online if you're wanting to see where our work is upto, add a revision or next task.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={Pagecover}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SectionHeadImg>
  </ContainerXL>

  <ContainerXL>
    <SectionHeadSecImg>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Cloud-based revisions.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        We know how important it is to create and revise hundreds of ideas quickly to find the best. Using cloud-based 
        design software to share moodboards and ideas, we can quickly work together anywhere in the world, using Figma, 
        to maintain blazing-fast, 2-day design turn arounds. Manage ideas and approvals online with Trello for complete 
        transparency and peace of mind you're making the most of your monthly design work.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={PagecoverSecondary}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SectionHeadSecImg>
    
  </ContainerXL>

  <ContainerXL>
    <SectionTextarea>
      <Fragment slot="title">Organic brand strategies.</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Ignite your brand's online presence with Aidxn Design's SEO-friendly strategies. 
        Experts in SEO designing brand strategies that not only captivate your audience 
        but also rank high in search engine results with ease. From keyword mockups and 
        to content category validation all before your brand hits the ground ensures a 
        smooth sailing brand launch or direction shift. Driving organic traffic as a key 
        pillar of your marketing plan.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={CoverTextarea}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconleft">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="simple-icons:googleads" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="titleleft">
        Google Search / Shopping / Display
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textleft">
        Zapier's powerful automation platform works directly
        with Velocity7. Automate tasks, synchronize data, 
        and reduce costs. All made simple with Velocity7 
        API connection.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconright">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="ph:device-mobile-camera-light" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="titleright">
        Meta (FB / IG)
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textright">
        All our Velocity sites are powered by Netlify's powerful, 
        load-balancing network of servers to deliver your content 
        to the end user faster than anyone else. Absolutely necessary
        with the cell networks available in Australia. Take back control 
        of your website's velocity with the speed of Velocity7 on Netlify's network.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconleft2">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="mdi:billboard" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="titleleft2">
        Billboards and Buses
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textleft2">
        Maximize your advertising effectiveness with Google Ads' 
        conversion tracking built deeply into Velocity7. Easily 
        track and measure conversions that matter most to your 
        business. Gain valuable insights into customer behavior 
        and optimize your ad strategy accordingly. With Google Ads' 
        comprehensive conversion tracking, you can make data-driven 
        decisions and drive higher ROI for your advertising efforts.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconright2">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="ph:file-search-light" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="titleright2">
        AI and Automation
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textright2">
        Streamline your payment process and boost sales with Stripe's 
        secure payment gateway. With one-click checkout, you can 
        provide a seamless payment experience for your customers, 
        reducing cart abandonment and driving conversions. Benefit 
        from Stripe's transparent pricing, and robust fraud prevention 
        from day one for your business. For frictionless payment experiences.
      </Fragment>      
    </SectionTextarea>
  </ContainerXL>

  <Container>

    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Turn Around in 14 Days.</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc"
        >We move as fast as possible with all design work as we know it makes all the difference. 
        Easily allowing for mockup revision and creative direction using Figma.
      </Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <Integrations />

  </Container>

  <Container>
    <Cta />
  </Container>


</Layout>
